  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK971">
<l>oḷiyoruvaṟ kuḷḷa veṟukkai yiḷiyoruvaṟ</l>
<l>kaḵtiṟantu vāḻu meṉal</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>One's light is the abundance of one's courage; one's darkness is the desire to live destitute of such (a state of mind.)</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
